formula: a(n) = (1/n)*(Sum_{d|n} mu(n/d)*binomial(6*d, d)) - 5*binomial(6*n, n)/(5*n+1) for n > 0. - _Andrew Howroyd_, May 02 2018
mathematica: a[n_] := DivisorSum[n, MoebiusMu[n/#] Binomial[6#, #]&]/n - 5 Binomial[6n, n]/(5n + 1);
